         <abstract id="aspace_2d59a2b105b1847a79a80d1782862ace">This collection consists of "problem books" - assignments set by Yale's graphic design faculty of graphic design "problems" to be creatively solved. The collection includes problems set by Paul Rand, Sheila Levrant de Bretteville, Pamela Hovland, Julian Bittiner, Barbara Glauber, John Gambell, and others.</abstract>
